snippet.title: F1® Manager 24 | Feature Focus - Races Brought To Life
snippet.description:
With mechanical failures, the addition of helicam, improvements to car behaviour and refreshed circuit visuals - F1® Manager 24 brings races to life in the most realistic F1® management experience to date! Learn more: https://www.f1manager.com/features/new/f1-races-brought-to-life

F1® Manager 24 releases on PC and consoles, July 23rd 2024. Pre-order Now: https://fron.dev/YT-F1M24-PO
